data.name: layCurrentBed.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT A.GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA,A.IPWON_DATE) GWA_NAME , A.DOCTOR , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, TRUNC(SYSDATE)) DOCTOR_NAME , A.HO_DONG1 , A.HO_CODE1 , A.BED_NO , B.SUNAME , A.IPWON_DATE , A.TOIWON_RES_DATE , DECODE (A.TOIWON_RES_DATE, NULL, 'N', 'Y') TOIWON_RES_YN , '' TOT_BED , A.PKINP1001 , '' TRANS_CNT , FN_NUR_LOAD_BUDOCTOR_LIST(:f_bunho, A.PKINP1001, TRUNC(SYSDATE)) BU_DOCTOR_LIST , A.HO_GRADE1 , A.KAIKEI_HODONG , A.KAIKEI_HOCODE FROM VW_OCS_INP1001_01 A , OUT0101 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND A.TOIWON_DATE IS NULL AND A.BUNHO = B.BUNHO

data.name: layHocodeBedno.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.BED_NO , A.BED_STATUS FROM BAS0253 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong AND A.HO_CODE = :f_ho_code AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN A.FROM_BED_DATE AND NVL(A.TO_BED_DATE, TO_DATE('9999/12/31', 'YYYY/MM/DD')) AND A.BED_STATUS != '05' ORDER BY 1

data.name: layMaxBedNo.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT MAX(A.HO_TOTAL_BED) FROM BAS0250 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong AND :f_ho_code_ymd BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND A.END_DATE /* AND A.START_DATE = ( SELECT MAX(Z.START_DATE) FROM BAS0250 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND Z.HO_CODE = A.HO_CODE AND Z.START_DATE <= :f_ho_code_ymd )*/

data.name: layHoSex.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HO_CODE , A.HO_SEX FROM BAS0250 A /*-- 병실정보*/ WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong AND A.HO_CODE = :f_ho_code AND :f_date BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND A.END_DATE
